title: open source drone
link: https://opensource.com/article/18/2/drone-projects
tag: drone
status: none
summary:
dronecode: https://www.dronecode.org/source_code/ BSD
            components include the PX4 autopilot flight control system,
            the MAVLink robotics communication toolkit, and the QGroundControl
            user interface for flight control, mission planning, and configuration
            
Paparazzi UAV: http://wiki.paparazziuav.org/wiki/Main_Page GPLv2: autonomous flight
ArduPilot: http://ardupilot.org/ GPLv3: split from dronecode due to license
           https://github.com/ArduPilot

LibrePilot: https://www.librepilot.org/site/index.html :GPLv3; control multi-copters and other radio-controlled drones
            https://bitbucket.org/librepilot/librepilot

Flone: http://flone.cc/ : GPLv3 
       https://github.com/aeracoop/flone

OpenDroneMap: http://opendronemap.org/ GPLv3 
              https://github.com/OpenDroneMap/OpenDroneMap/wiki

https://github.com/MatrixPilot/MatrixPilot
http://adapilot.likeabird.eu/
